**Benefits**:
- Function naming now clearly indicates what each validation does
- Improved readability of `processClaim` by extracting multi-line validation into a single, well-named function call
- Consistent pattern with existing validation functions (`validateItemInPolicy`)
- Easier to test validation logic in isolation if needed
- Reduced cognitive load when reading the main function logic

